# screen sharing
# http://technonstop.com/screen-commands-for-terminal-sharing
screen -d -R share_session
screen -x share_session



screen -ls ## list session
screen -wipe ## remove dead session




split display horizontally	C-a S
split display vertically	C-a | or C-a V (for the vanilla vertical screen patch)
jump to next display region	C-a tab
remove current region	C-a X
remove all regions but the current one	C-a Q

